00:42:28.350 --> 00:42:30.180
Le grand blanc called us that.

00:42:30.180 --> 00:42:34.420
And the Negroes called
us that, the petit blanc.

00:42:34.420 --> 00:42:38.540
We are not grand
people, but small ones.

00:42:38.540 --> 00:42:42.410
And my grandfather, he
was trying to lift us up.

00:42:42.410 --> 00:42:45.770
It is too bad with
that White League.

00:42:45.770 --> 00:42:49.380
But they ain't nothing we can
do about it now, now is there?"

00:42:52.300 --> 00:42:53.615
Thank you very much.

00:42:53.615 --> 00:42:55.835
[APPLAUSE]

